OL,3,CExplosion at military weapons factory
OL,5,FA BAE Systems spokesperson said: "We
OL,6,Fcan confirm that there was an incident
OL,7,Fat our Glascoed facility in Wales this
OL,8,Fmorning.
OL,10,F"Tried and tested safety protocols
OL,11,Fwere immediately enacted and emergency
OL,12,Fservices attended the site.
OL,14,F"All personnel are accounted for and
OL,15,Fthere were no injuries. Our emergency
OL,16,Fresponse team continue to monitor the
OL,17,Ffacility and a full investigation has
OL,18,Fbeen launched."
